room_title: Escape room "Elf Myself" by Breakout Escape Rooms in Detroit
room_description: You always wanted to be an Elf. You love green, pointed shoes, singing and have the maturity of a house fly. Luckily, due to the increase of Elves going into dentistry, shoe making, and baking in trees, the demand is high and standards are low. Do you have what it takes to become an Elvin Toy Maker?
